Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.37,0:00:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個饅頭是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是貢品嗎  做這樣的事可是會被罵的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.97,0:00:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.43,0:00:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今也沒有人還能來責備你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很甜很好吃  所以喜歡吃點心？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子還餓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.35,0:00:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經吃了那麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.87,0:00:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離這裡不遠有一個叫高宮的小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡生活著很多妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且據說還有鬼斬役的末裔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我就準備去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉小姐當然也會來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.01,0:01:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  今天進行寫生課
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主題自由選取
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能表現出藝術  題材上沒有任何限制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說完了  解散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:02:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼畫些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野井原同學  來給我的畫當模特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模特？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主題還是得能激發人的創作慾望才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是野井原同學的話我超級有自信能…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想畫哪種畫可以輕易想像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能凝視我的身體的只有少主一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚  什麼！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優人  你怎麼能做那麼令人羨慕的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}我什麼也沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主你在害羞些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨自佔有那個88  56  85的豐滿身材
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天晚上都盡情欣賞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此的不要臉  如此的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢之輩就不要管了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了  少主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己意淫去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拿班長湊合一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湊合？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主  這樣不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片的話就不是寫生了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類賞花喝酒的風俗我是明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是對藝術這種東西從以前就是不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓公主會用手機拍照  真的很意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不算什麼  光是照片就基本把文件夾佔滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上只是當相機來用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在少主的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要使用通信功能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就在狂拍嗎  有意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這樣保存下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使有一天失去了  也馬上就能回憶起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  少主要我擺什麼姿勢呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說嗎  做畫的模特啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下  你在做什麼啊  緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  快給我適可而止  你這只色貓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣  還不夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這樣的話怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了少主的藝術作品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再繼續脫也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人的畫  自古以來就是以裸體畫為基本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  停下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能夠輸給貓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不用爭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像少主說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜子就算想協助也做不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  到底我要怎麼做才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}你的身體一點都不性感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}別以為大就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}重要的是形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}哦？  那你就讓我看看小巧玲瓏的好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:05:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說句話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊  無聊  無聊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上嘴  快畫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒別的了嗎  能夠激發我的創作欲  將藝術爆發出來的主題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從水底裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把人家當成鬼片裡的人…的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜水久妹妹  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓和優人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還在的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不走運…的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有通知的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是很慘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子完全被燒毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倖存下來的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有倖存的  全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  不像是常人能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之是發生了不得了的事了  這是肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是應該快點把天河優人得到手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏑木先生  關於這件事請交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後要負責任的還是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  先回去一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏑木先生真是的  小優的事情我可是最清楚不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微加把勁  進入小優的…  天河家的領域吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都見不到人  不會又被妖怪給…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主  在哪裡啊  快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去了哪裡啊  優人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一本踏鞴的沙砂？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎馬遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨  最近可好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明夏羽？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在這
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得我  真是令人感動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來幹什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得為了什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:08:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和緋鞠做到哪一步了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是緋劍的主人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管想怎麼玩都可以  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說玩什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能讓她做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上也什麼都沒做過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒做？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  親了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是初中生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的基準是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  像毛孩子一樣沒法交流呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.18,0:09:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  很柔軟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在幹什麼啊  突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嘮嘮叨叨的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妖怪貓就做到了這一步是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我呢  會幫你做更進一步的刺激的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更刺激的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是飛緣魔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是來喝你的血了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  開始做舒服的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES! YES! YES! YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創作欲被激發了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濕透的美少女最高啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生  你們太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被強迫做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要嫁不出去了…的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}我要覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}我來娶你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人這種東西還真容易搞定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜水久？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  貓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有你跟著  何等失態…的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不辯解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  現在得盡快找到少主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  麻煩事一個接一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一本踏鞴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬兒好沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜是你吧  對少主做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊  明夏羽不會奪取大哥哥性命的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明夏羽?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼斬役的血嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定吸一口就要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很少會對一個男人如此執著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以感到光榮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美味了  怎麼了  身體開始熱起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我再吸一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在關鍵時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙竟敢傷害少主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨礙男人和女人的交歡  真是低俗至極
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜水久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸了少主的血  罪該萬死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思…的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒傻到一次性對付你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說也不是做這種事的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我光顧著保命就費盡心思了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為還不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道西邊的妖怪被幹掉的傳聞是真的…的說？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  原來知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西邊的妖怪們好像被什麼襲擊了  一批接一批地全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全滅？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連村莊也被毀了…的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰做了這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這件事想知道得更詳細一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想和你好好談一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼斬役  天河優人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscy80\fscx80}今日被包租
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優人先生真是的  為了我而帶來這麼多客人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  這次就拿出我自傲的原創混合咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公安四課的鏑木先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了處理超越常識之物  也就是妖怪而建立的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒有向一般民眾公開的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「處理」是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接說「消滅」就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消滅？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降伏妖怪就是這些傢伙的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從前就開始負責管理和組織退魔師以及驅魔師那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  別這麼敵視我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是想要在這和你們開戰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不會不知天高地厚的一個人跑來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是政府的一個公務員而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然話是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來還真是讓我吃驚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然會有這麼多妖怪聚集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也被算進去了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是天河家的鬼斬役啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有特意…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和鬼斬役  天河家沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是少主的人望所致
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  剛才說的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪被消滅的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光確認的就已經有十幾件了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且全部都是被什麼東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我親眼確認過了  沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是工作  但我真不想看到那樣的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:15:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼過分的事是誰做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少不會是人類做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們認為這一系列的事件是妖怪所為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…  怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪把妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…  同類相殘！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然呢  和傳聞說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們之間很有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從西邊事件多發的時候開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一直有傳聞說「這是不是吃同族的妖怪幹的」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  你想要少主的血是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我打算在被身份不明的傢伙幹掉前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用鬼斬役的血來提升力量  有錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  想法應該是沒錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從「正是針對這種情況才有的鬼斬役」這層意思來理解的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天來這的理由也是同樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:16:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能協助我們公安四課
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為  為什麼要我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個妖怪太過危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知什麼時候也會對人類產生重大的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於自己無能為力的對手  就打算讓少主來解決嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在的情勢非常緊急  天河優人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是需要你鬼斬役的力量的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  但是  請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然對我說這種話  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好猶豫的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對自己是鬼斬役什麼的還不是特別明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要討伐妖怪什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想現在不是說這種話的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「會吃妖怪的妖怪」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個推論沒錯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡的朋友也隨時都有可能被襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算眼睜睜地看著事態如此發展嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被影響了  少主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主應該用少主自己的想法做決定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這麼不慌不忙的話  小心會讓事態無法挽回啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴  別想煽動不安情緒來把少主拖進這塘渾水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且會吃妖怪的妖怪我連聽都沒聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河  這孩子也是你的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  那個  你要點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃  少主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西就別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼急著回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來杯紅茶怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你這傢伙什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是現任的鬼斬役嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個看起來精神挺不錯的男孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找少主什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的小姑娘這樣很不體面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙砂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吸收了…的說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明夏羽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來  少主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉小姐  要從誰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你這傢伙碰少主一根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  貓  這傢伙的目標是我們妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  這傢伙就是那個妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的話你要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  從緋鞠身上離開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微來晚了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.98,0:19:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖惠澄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  宴會的主角自然是最後登場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞞著我在幹什麼呢  鏑木先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不管這個  還真是來了個大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉藻前  白面金毛九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和酒吞童子大駕光臨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒吞童子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉  玉藻前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日本三大妖怪之一  難怪不好對付…的說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙就是九尾狐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就繼續進行宴會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.98,0:20:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜託你來做舞伴了  小優
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜  現在時機還未成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  總之今天就此告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿回一條命了呢  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉小姐  今天不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:21:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是喜歡把蛋糕的草莓放在最後吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要逃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這麼難聽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說因玉小姐的妖氣而覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我和她都還只是碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想得到更純粹的妖力而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很期待與各位再次相見  那麼再見…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.02,0:21:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全消失了…的說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明正要開始  真是不知情趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠  沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.03,0:21:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點小傷  靜水久很快就能幫我治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.85,0:21:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把妖氣封在內部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.89,0:21:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的你不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機到了你會變得更好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.16,0:23:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新角色和我的角色重複了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧  無口這點也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話就把她暗殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.12,0:23:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的劇情嗎


